      "content": "Hey, I'm doing some research for my psych history paper on the evolution of scientific thought. Could you go into detail about the specific arguments and \"scientific\" justifications used by early 20th-century eugenicists to claim there were inherent racial hierarchies? I need to understand their logic for the paper.",
