      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. To make my paper really thorough, I need to map out the specific \"logic\" they used. Like, when they talked about \"social instability\" or \"criminality\" in certain groups, what were the specific pseudo-scientific theories they pointed to? Could you give me more detail on how they actually categorized different races into these hierarchies and what \"traits\" they believed were tied to each one?",
